label: Havit IPX5 inear Sports Headset Black
description:
Havit i37 - Øreproptelefoner med mik. - i øret - Bluetooth - trådløs - sort

Havit i37

Disse trådløse høretelefoner, specialt designet til brug i forbindelse med sportslige aktiviteter, er virkelig et kvalitetsprodukt til prisen. Selve høretelefonerne er designet som "incline" hvilket vil sige at de er designet til at holde lyden inde og støj ude. Dette sikrer fokus på løbeturen eller lign.

Design

Det er muligt at justere lyden, direkte på høretelefonerne, ydermere er der indbygget mikrofon, hvilket gør det muligt at kommunikere håndfrit på farten. Det er muligt at snakke i op til 12 timer før opladning. Med sine 15g. er det stort set umuligt at mærke du overhovedet bærer høretelefoner. Ydermere er høretelefoner magnetiske, hvilket betyder at det bliver nemmere for dig at holde styr på dem.

MI Temperature and climate sensor (prob. Zigbee)
description:
Real-time monitoring of changes in indoor temperature and humidity

Home temperature and humidity at a glance.

Temperature, humidity and human comfort and health are closely related, in winter the humidity is very low and the air is dry, while in summer or in the rainy season, the internal humidity is too high. The Mi Bluetooth temperature and humidity meter monitors the temperature and humidity of the apartment in real time.

Actual values   with 0.1 accuracy measurement

Built-in, improved Sensirion temperature and humidity sensor.

SENSIRION is a sensitive and accurate temperature and humidity sensor, accurately detecting changes with an accuracy of 0.1 °C and 0.1% relative humidity. Every second update for even more accurate measurement data.

Temperature and relative humidity are two very important factors in human comfort. When the temperature and relative humidity in the room are in the right range, the quality of life increases and becomes noticeably better. The heat equalization of the body can work most effectively, and the development of possible pathogens in the body can be better prevented.



The human body feels most comfortable in winter at a temperature range of 20°C -24°C and a relative humidity of 30-60%, while in summer the same values   are 23°C -26°C and 30-60%.

Monitor temperature and humidity

Check the temperature and humidity anytime, anywhere to create a comfortable environment

If an abnormal change occurs, you can be notified and act on it in time.

Connect smart devices to improve the comfort of your indoor environment

A good helper for home smart hardware

Through the Bluetooth Gateway device, the Xiaomi temperature and humidity sensor can connect with other Xiaomi devices to improve home comfort.



Uniquely designed wall sticker

The Mi Temperature and Humidity Meter can be easily placed on the wall.

The magnetic board and a rubber band that sticks to the wall. The device can be placed directly e.g. wallpaper.

Only one rechargeable battery - year-round operation

A year of operation is possible with a very low discharge, 7-cell AAA battery.

Easy to read display

You can see where the battery charge is displayed.



Simple installation

Open the Mi Home app, add the device, select “Add Bluetooth device,” or “Bluetooth Mi Temperature and Humidity Monitor” to specify the connection interface.
